    <description>While I understand that it varies a great deal from one expansion to the next, overall, melee are far more powerful than casters, with casters having only a few brief periods where they overpower melee.&amp;nbsp; (This is why I'm going melee this time around...)&amp;nbsp; There is no reason to further increase melee power vs casters, they are already overpowered and were overpowered all the way through the game, with maybe a short break in luclin where caster dps actually was as good as melees on raids at least.&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
